text: Juan Jeraldino Jil (born 6 December 1995) is a Chilean footballer that currently plays for Deportes Vallenar in the Segunda División de Chile. His brother Ignacio Jeraldino is also a footballer. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean footballers Category:Primera B de Chile players Category:Unión San Felipe footballers Category:Association football forwards
